location.fullValue: 879 Great Egret Circle SW UNIT E

data.description: Opportunity Knocks with a Price Reduction! Coastal 3 Bedroom Condo features stellar Pond & Golf Course Views with a Screened-In Balcony. Premier Location. Sunny open floor plan with a 25' living & dining area accented by its vaulted ceiling. Tasteful LVP flooring throughout added last year, including the bedrooms. No carpet here! The White Kitchen offers a peninsula with bar stool seating and comes stocked with dishes and cookware. Fresh new paint in the Master Bedroom with its sliding glass door to enjoy the tranquility & the privacy of the balcony. It has a sizeable walk-in closet and its bath offers a walk-in shower. The 2 guest bedrooms are up front with their own bathroom, providing space for all. Other bonuses are a kitchen pantry, a full size washer & dryer, and an outdoor storage closet near the front door for your beach & fishing gear. Superb 2nd floor in a 4 plex with no one above you. Never a rental. Furnished & move-in ready with a pleasing color palette. Worthy of a full time residence, 2nd home or rental investment. Quiet location with no buildings across the street. The entire complex is clean and well maintained. Two pools, hot tubs and tennis are just a few minutes walk. Live the beach lifestyle in this popular golf community, surrounded by lush landscaping and ponds that attract wildlife. Located about 12 minutes to the pristine white sand of Sunset Beach. For avid golfers, play Sandpiper's 27 hole course or dozens more local courses. Groceries, banks, restaurants and medical are all close by. Fulfill your dreams of having a place at the beach with Myrtle Beach's entertainment only 30 minutes away and a short 45 minutes to historic Wilmington.
